# ============================================================================
# Package Manifest for AG News Text Classification
# ============================================================================
# Project: AG News Text Classification (ag-news-text-classification)
# Description: Specification of files included in source distribution
# Author: Võ Hải Dũng
# Email: vohaidung.work@gmail.com
# License: MIT
# ============================================================================
#
# Purpose:
#   This manifest specifies which files should be included in or excluded
#   from the source distribution when building the package with setuptools.
#   Ensures proper package distribution with all necessary files while
#   excluding development artifacts and large binary files.
#
# Syntax Reference:
#   include <pattern>                   - Include matching files
#   recursive-include <dir> <pattern>   - Include recursively from directory
#   exclude <pattern>                   - Exclude matching files
#   recursive-exclude <dir> <pattern>   - Exclude recursively from directory
#   global-exclude <pattern>            - Exclude pattern globally
#   graft <dir>                         - Include entire directory
#   prune <dir>                         - Exclude entire directory
#
# Build Commands:
#   Source distribution:  python setup.py sdist
#   Wheel distribution:   python setup.py bdist_wheel
#   Both:                 python -m build
#   Verify:               python setup.py sdist --dry-run --verbose
#
# References:
#   - https://packaging.python.org/en/latest/guides/using-manifest-in/
#   - https://setuptools.pypa.io/en/latest/userguide/miscellaneous.html
#   - https://peps.python.org/pep-0517/
#
# ============================================================================

