#   - OS-specific files
#   - Environment secrets
#   - Training logs and checkpoints
#
# Estimated Package Size:
#   - Source distribution: 50-100 MB
#   - Wheel distribution: 30-60 MB
#   - Without data and models: manageable for PyPI
#
# Installation Workflow:
#   1. Install package: pip install ag-news-text-classification
#   2. Download data: python scripts/setup/download_all_data.py
#   3. Download models: python scripts/setup/download_pretrained_models.py
#   4. Run setup: ag-news-setup
#
# Verification:
#   python setup.py sdist --dry-run --verbose | grep -E "adding|copying"
